01:05:55.820 --> 01:05:59.900
our politics, our
economics, the data--

01:05:59.900 --> 01:06:02.900
that these are just
the thinnest of veneers

01:06:02.900 --> 01:06:05.570
over the human drama.

01:06:05.570 --> 01:06:08.240
And again, it's really
messy and uncomfortable

01:06:08.240 --> 01:06:09.740
